  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"_8Pz3U_K\">性别区分的根本依据是产生不同的配子,雄性产生精子(数量多,体积小较灵活的配子),雌性产生卵子(数量少,体积大较笨重的配子),无关乎染色体和第一性征,<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=109510339&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B5%B7%E9%A9%AC&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">海马<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>雄性受孕,但实质是雌性将卵注入雄性体内受精,新穴虫雌性则是吸取雄性的精子自己受孕</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
